# InfluexAI environment templates — do not put real secrets here.
#
# Choose the template that matches your workflow:
#
#   .env.local.example   — safe local development defaults (copy → .env.local)
#   .env.staging.example — staging / mutating QA (copy → .env.local)
#
# Full runbook: docs/environment-safety.md
# Smoke tests:  docs/SMOKE_TEST_CHECKLIST.md
#
# Validate a template (no secrets printed):
#   node scripts/check-env-safety.mjs --example .env.local.example
#   node scripts/check-env-safety.mjs --example .env.staging.example
#
# Check your local .env.local (signal categories only, no values):
#   node scripts/check-env-safety.mjs --file .env.local
